These are Puzzles for 1x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-1::.
There are 6 different nationalities: colombian, spanish, japanese, malaysian, chinese, pakistani
1. the spanish is the spanish##1
2. the japanese is on the left or right of the colombian##3
3. the spanish is somewhere to the right of the chinese##5
4. the colombian is not to the left of the pakistani##8
5. the japanese is on the far left or far right##3
6. the colombian is on the right of the malaysian##1
7. the malaysian is between the colombian and the pakistani##2
8. the spanish is on the left or right of the pakistani##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |      4       |   5    |   6   |
| Nationality   | chinese | spanish | pakistani | malaysian | colombian | japanese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-2::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  fisherman, scientist, mechanic, electrician, bartender, police-officer
1. the scientist is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
2. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
3. the fisherman is on the left or right of the electrician##3
4. the police-officer is on the far right##1
5. the fisherman is somewhere to the left of the electrician##5
6. the electrician is not to the right of the bartender##8
7. the mechanic is on the left or right of the bartender##3
8. the police-officer is on the right of the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |  3   |    4     |   5    |   6   |
| Job   | fisherman | electrician | scientist | mechanic | bartender | police-officer |

