.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-3::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: helicopter, tram, car, roller, bike, bus
1. the person driving the helicopter is not to the right of the person driving the bike##8
2. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
3. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |   3   |     4      |  5  |   6    |
| Transport   | roller | bus | car | helicopter | bike | tram |

