.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-5::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: daffodil, begonia, balloon-flower, iris, orchid, sunflower
 1. the person who growsiris is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who growsiris is not to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##8
 3. the person who growssunflower is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the left of the person who growsorchid##5
 5. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
 6. the person who growsbegonia is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person who growsiris##2
 7. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person who growsiris##7
 8. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdaffodil##5
 9. the person who growsiris is not to the right of the person who growsiris##8
10. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |    4     |   5   |       6       |
| Flower   | sunflower | daffodil | balloon-flower | begonia | iris | orchid |

