.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-7::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: tea, iced-tea, fanta, juice, sprite, water
1. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
4. the person drinking fanta is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
5. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
6. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking tea##2
7. the person drinking tea is not to the left of the person drinking juice##8
8. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
9. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |    5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | juice | fanta | sprite | tea | iced-tea | water |

