.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-9::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: october, april, june, september, november, may
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##8
6. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |      2       |     3     |        4        |    5    |    6     |
| Birthday   | june | may | april | november | october | september |

