.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-11::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: lacrosse, weightlifting, skiing, basketball, biathlon, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##8
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##8
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's sport is basketball##7
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is lacrosse##7
7. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
8. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |      3      |   4    |    5    |    6    |
| Sport   | basketball | water-polo | weightlifting | lacrosse | biathlon | skiing |

