.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-13::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: animation, martial-arts, adventure, time-travel, fantasy, documentary
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##8
4. the person watching documentary movies is not to the right of the person watching adventure movies##8
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
6. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##5
7. the person watching documentary movies is in an odd position##4
8. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person watching animation movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3    |   4    |    5     |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | animation | documentary | adventure | martial-arts | time-travel |

